  dcterms:description "Spreadsheet-fidelity ontology derived directly from the cleaned EDI Hub+ taxonomy columns. Each distinct cleaned tag value is represented as a concept under one of four top-level categories. Alternative labels are limited to variants observed during cleaning (normalisation log)." .

